WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.160
I am so excited today to talk to you about Quantum RF at Hello Gorgeous Med Spa in Oswego, Illinois.

00:03.160 --> 00:05.400
It's designed to tighten, lift, and contour

00:05.400 --> 00:08.120
with the latest innovation in non-surgical skin

00:08.120 --> 00:08.960
rejuvenation.

00:08.960 --> 00:12.080
This advanced treatment uses fractionated bipolar

00:12.080 --> 00:15.520
radiofrequency to stimulate collagen and firm skin,

00:15.520 --> 00:18.280
treating areas like the face, neck, arms,

00:18.280 --> 00:19.640
abdomen, and thighs.

00:19.640 --> 00:22.080
A tiny cannula delivers controlled heat

00:22.080 --> 00:25.520
under the skin to tighten tissue and improve elasticity.

00:25.520 --> 00:27.560
Patients see immediate improvements

00:27.560 --> 00:29.720
with results continuing as the skin

00:29.720 --> 00:32.480
naturally remodels over several weeks.

00:32.480 --> 00:35.440
Schedule your Quantum RF consultation today

00:35.440 --> 00:38.360
and experience firmer, more youthful skin.
